short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Forces the browser to the front of the screen when the user is in a Not Ready or Dispositioning status and there is a call in queue.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Plugin for Max Contact to allow the browser to be pulled into the agent view when a call is in queue.
